additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Alcohol Denat, Butane, Isopropyl Alcohol, Picaridin, Isopropyl Myristate.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Not to be used for any purpose or in any manner, contrary to this label unless authorised. Keep out of reach of children. Extremely flammable. Do not spray directly on exposed food, water, food preparation areas or food utensils. Do not spray near naked flame, heat or any incandescent material. Do not smoke during use. Avoid inhaling spray mist. Intentional misuse by deliberately concentrating and inhaling contents can be harmful or fatal. If rash or irritation occurs, discontinue use. If poisoning occurs, contact a doctor or Poisons Information Centre. Phone Australia 13 11 26.
